'''Blossom Chukwujekwu''' yin aihundatọ Naijilia tọn, he basi dohia aihun etọn titan. To owhe 2015 ẹ mon àjò he yọn hugan yi to [[Africa Magic Viewers Choice Awards]].

==Bẹjeji Gbezan Etọn Tọn po Wepiplọn po==
E ji chukwudi Echezoma Chukwujekwu to Abọ̀húsun azan 4tọ owhe 1983 to [[Benin City]], [[Edo]] to Naijilia to Dr. I. E po Evangelist J. C. Chukwujekwu, 
Blossom Chukwujekwu yin sunnu tintan to sunnu awe he mẹjitọ tọn do lẹ me. Ogbe [[Otolo]] to Anambra Huwaji-agewaji Naijilia tọn.
